## Output Format

JSON object:
- iteration_count: how many iterations were run
- metric_trajectory: array of {iteration, metric_before, metric_after}
- variance_trend: "decreasing" | "stable" | "increasing"
- prediction_accuracy: array of {iteration, predicted, actual, delta}
- learning_convergence: "converging" if iterations align, "diverging" if spread
- comparison_note: what the iterations collectively reveal about the process
